title: Barrett-Jackson LIVE Auction
overview: The only view better than the water and sand is the sight of the cars rolling down the block at this year's Barrett-Jackson auction. Tune in for collector cars that are out of this world as Barrett-Jackson lands in Scottsdale, Arizona. Barrett-Jackson is in Scottsdale with some of the best cars the auction has seen yet. From collector classics to modern marvels, Scottsdale has it all.
